@startuml packages-modelhub
!include ../_includes/style.iuml

title Diagramme de package — disposition source du sous-système IA

' Les packages UML mappent 1:1 vers les répertoires du filesystem. Les
' dépendances suivent les vrais imports TS (flèches plus légères = optionnel / fail-soft).

package "src/shared" {
  package "RoutingTypes" as PKG_SHARED {
    [Signature]
    [BehavioralSignature]
    [CompetenceBranch]
    [RoutingConfig]
    [DiagnosticAxis]
    [COMPETENCE_TREE]
  }
}
note right of PKG_SHARED
  Contrats figés — chaque type routing /
  caractérisation vit ici.
end note

package "src/main/modelhub" as PKG_MH {

  package "routing" as PKG_R {
    [scorers] as PKG_R_SCORERS
    [sandbox] as PKG_R_SBX
    [questions] as PKG_R_QUESTIONS
    component "characterizeAll\n(bulk single-pass,\n2026-05-23)\n+ archiveServerLog\nsession par modèle\n(2026-05-24)" as M_CH_ALL
    component "characterizeRunner\n+ filtre non-chat 3 niveaux\n(arch / nom /\nadaptatif, 2026-05-24)" as M_CH_RUN
    component "characterizeTree" as M_CH_TREE
    component "staircase" as M_STAIR
    component "freegen\n(split 2 phases,\n2026-05-22)" as M_FG
    component "embedderCli\n(2026-05-23)" as M_EMB_CLI
    component "routeDecision\n+ routeByVectors\n+ classifyQuery" as M_ROUTE
    component "embed / embedDetect /\nembedProject" as M_EMBED_CORE
    component "chat\n(ChatClient,\npas de timeout\nwall-clock +\ncapture\nreasoning_content,\n2026-05-24)" as M_CHAT
    component "signatureStore" as M_SIG
    component "freeMemory" as M_MEM
    component "routingCommon" as M_COMMON
  }

  package "mcp" as PKG_MCP {
    component "tools/" as PKG_MCP_TOOLS
    component "server" as M_MCP_SRV
    component "registry" as M_MCP_REG
  }

  component "runners/" as PKG_RUNNERS
  component "embedderLifecycle\n(mode serveur,\nqueries routing)" as M_EMB_LC
  component "modelLogStore\n(2026-05-23,\narchive par session\n2026-05-24)\n.ts/<fichier>.log\n.ts/<fichier>.<ISO>.log\n.ts/<fichier>.error" as M_LOG_STORE
  component "routingConfig" as M_RC
  component "launchModel /\nlistModelFiles /\nshardFs" as M_FILES
}

package "src/renderer/" as PKG_RND {
  package "modelhub" as PKG_RND_MH {
    component "radar/" as PKG_RND_RADAR
  }
  package "components/dialogs/components" as PKG_RND_SET {
    component "SettingsAI" as M_UI_SET
  }
}

' Flux câblé (dépendances d'imports TS, dashed = optionnel/fail-soft)
M_CH_ALL --> M_CH_RUN : runCharacterization\nrunFreeGenGenerate\nrunFreeGenProject
M_CH_ALL --> M_EMB_CLI : resolveEmbedderCliFn\n(par run bulk)
M_CH_ALL ..> M_LOG_STORE : appendErrorLog\narchiveServerLog\n(rotation par modèle)
M_CH_RUN ..> M_LOG_STORE : archiveServerLog\n(CARACTÉRISER unique)
M_CH_RUN --> M_CH_TREE
M_CH_RUN --> M_RC
M_CH_RUN ..> PKG_R_SBX : seam runSandbox
M_CH_TREE --> M_STAIR
M_CH_TREE ..> M_FG : generateFreeGenText\n(phase 1, pas d'embedder)
M_STAIR --> PKG_R_SCORERS
M_STAIR ..> PKG_R_SBX : runCheck → sandbox
M_FG --> M_EMBED_CORE
M_EMB_CLI --> PKG_RUNNERS : dérive llama-embedding\ndepuis le runner llama-server
M_ROUTE --> M_EMBED_CORE
M_ROUTE --> M_MEM
M_ROUTE --> M_COMMON
M_ROUTE --> M_EMB_LC : ensureEmbedderReady\n(queries interactives)
M_EMB_LC --> M_FILES : launchModelByPath
PKG_RUNNERS ..> M_LOG_STORE : appendServerLog\n(hook logChunk dans launch.ts)
M_MCP_REG --> PKG_MCP_TOOLS
PKG_MCP_TOOLS --> M_ROUTE : models.route
PKG_MCP_TOOLS --> M_FILES : list / spawn

PKG_RND_RADAR ..> PKG_SHARED : type-only
PKG_RND_MH ..> PKG_SHARED : type-only
M_UI_SET ..> M_RC : (type côté renderer)
PKG_R ..> PKG_SHARED
PKG_MCP ..> PKG_SHARED

note right of PKG_R_QUESTIONS
  Embarqué via electron-builder
  extraResources, asar-unpacked
  dans les builds packagés (pour
  que l'emplacement Tests Maestria
  puisse les ouvrir sur disque).
end note

note bottom of PKG_SHARED
  Le renderer ET le processus main importent
  ce module — garde type-only côté renderer
  pour éviter de bundler du code Node.
end note

@enduml
